{"tid":1535243,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"換個想法，一至五正常，六日抗爭。唔罷工都冇影響","createTime":"2019-09-03T09:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T10:30:36.000Z","uid":11454,"like":48,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0feaa592355c8f36cfc5da34bf5fa68595dfd9","tid":1535243,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:41:11.000Z","msg":"罷工罷課係要長時間，用月計先有效<br />\n得罪講句，香港人無依個膽量<br />\n<br />\n一兩日既罷工注定失敗<br />\n<br />\n既然政府要拖長玩<br />\n不如順勢週末打番主線行動<br />\n一直都係咁玩<br />\n平日主力文宣，<br />\n<br />\n體力，民氣都得以延續<br />\n何必急在一時<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9b82ec999c16f0b6f0a6751c6ba062bfbe83fe","tid":1535243,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:41:17.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fb714374221ed2ab011d02e08dfecd116a6d355","tid":1535243,"uid":31587,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:41:53.000Z","msg":"平日打支線<br />\n周末打主線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b080f908c1c6f63dfac2c9846c6d9970666b37","tid":1535243,"uid":19165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:42:08.000Z","msg":"支持 持之以恆先係良策"},{"pid":"b0d41cc53d6e712bd017320a2200dfad437662a1","tid":1535243,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6cfee5e5c132bf037b8842eae2eb01defe901b5","tid":1535243,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:43:30.000Z","msg":"全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n6. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n7. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n8. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n9. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n10. 不要說推，試著將呢成個訊息copy and paste嚟推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n額外事件：練美國歌國。事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"c97ad729f524eaf07a30700b9008b94f32546d52","tid":1535243,"uid":221055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T09:44:42.000Z","msg":"其實諗真啲香港人真係好痴線，星期六日全副武裝，星期一至五可以如常生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊有暴動係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d528108abf39df94813d6dab50aa240ce2e32f","tid":1535243,"uid":11454